{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.1","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 35:1","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.034.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.035.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">C\u00e9l\u00e9bration solennelle de la P\u00e2que sous Josias<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-19: cf. 2 R 23:21-25. (2 Ch 30. Esd 6:19-22.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.35.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>\n    Josias c\u00e9l\u00e9bra la P\u00e2que en l\u2019honneur de l\u2019\u00c9ternel \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem, et l\u2019on immola la P\u00e2que le quatorzi\u00e8me jour du premier mois.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35","name":"2 Chroniques 35","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.2","name":"2 Chroniques 35:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.34.33","name":"2 Chroniques 34:33","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.34.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.2","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 35:2","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.035.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.035.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.35.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Il \u00e9tablit les sacrificateurs dans leurs fonctions, et les encouragea au service de la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35","name":"2 Chroniques 35","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.3","name":"2 Chroniques 35:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.1","name":"2 Chroniques 35:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.3","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 35:3","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.035.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.035.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.35.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Il dit aux L\u00e9vites qui enseignaient tout Isra\u00ebl et qui \u00e9taient consacr\u00e9s \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel: Placez l\u2019arche sainte dans la maison qu\u2019a b\u00e2tie Salomon, fils de David, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl; vous n\u2019avez plus \u00e0 la porter sur l\u2019\u00e9paule. Servez maintenant l\u2019\u00c9ternel, votre Dieu, et son peuple d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35","name":"2 Chroniques 35","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.4","name":"2 Chroniques 35:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.2","name":"2 Chroniques 35:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.4","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 35:4","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.035.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.035.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.35.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Tenez-vous pr\u00eats, selon vos maisons paternelles, selon vos divisions, comme l\u2019ont r\u00e9gl\u00e9 par \u00e9crit David, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, et Salomon, son fils;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35","name":"2 Chroniques 35","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.5","name":"2 Chroniques 35:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.3","name":"2 Chroniques 35:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.5","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 35:5","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.035.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.035.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.35.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>occupez vos places dans le sanctuaire, d\u2019apr\u00e8s les diff\u00e9rentes maisons paternelles de vos fr\u00e8res les fils du peuple, et d\u2019apr\u00e8s la classification des maisons paternelles des L\u00e9vites.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35","name":"2 Chroniques 35","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.6","name":"2 Chroniques 35:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.4","name":"2 Chroniques 35:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.6","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 35:6","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.035.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.035.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.35.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Immolez la P\u00e2que, sanctifiez-vous, et pr\u00e9parez-la pour vos fr\u00e8res, en vous conformant \u00e0 la parole de l\u2019\u00c9ternel prononc\u00e9e par Mo\u00efse.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35","name":"2 Chroniques 35","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.7","name":"2 Chroniques 35:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.5","name":"2 Chroniques 35:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.7","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 35:7","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.035.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.035.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.35.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Josias donna aux gens du peuple, \u00e0 tous ceux qui se trouvaient l\u00e0, des agneaux et des chevreaux au nombre de trente mille, le tout pour la P\u00e2que, et trois mille b\u0153ufs; cela fut pris sur les biens du roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35","name":"2 Chroniques 35","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.8","name":"2 Chroniques 35:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.6","name":"2 Chroniques 35:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.8","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 35:8","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.035.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.035.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.35.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Ses chefs firent de bon gr\u00e9 un pr\u00e9sent au peuple, aux sacrificateurs et aux L\u00e9vites. Hilkija, Zacharie, et Jehiel, princes de la maison de Dieu, donn\u00e8rent aux sacrificateurs pour la P\u00e2que deux mille six cents agneaux et trois cents b\u0153ufs.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35","name":"2 Chroniques 35","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.9","name":"2 Chroniques 35:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.7","name":"2 Chroniques 35:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.9","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 35:9","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.035.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.035.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.35.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Conania, Schemaeja et Nethaneel, ses fr\u00e8res, Haschabia, Je\u00efel et Jozabad, chefs des L\u00e9vites, donn\u00e8rent aux L\u00e9vites pour la P\u00e2que cinq mille agneaux et cinq cents b\u0153ufs.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35","name":"2 Chroniques 35","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.10","name":"2 Chroniques 35:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.8","name":"2 Chroniques 35:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.10","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 35:10","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.035.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.035.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.35.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Le service s\u2019organisa, et les sacrificateurs et les L\u00e9vites occup\u00e8rent leur place, selon leurs divisions, d\u2019apr\u00e8s l\u2019ordre du roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35","name":"2 Chroniques 35","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.11","name":"2 Chroniques 35:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.9","name":"2 Chroniques 35:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.11","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 35:11","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.035.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.035.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.35.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Ils immol\u00e8rent la P\u00e2que; les sacrificateurs r\u00e9pandirent le sang qu\u2019ils recevaient de la main des L\u00e9vites, et les L\u00e9vites d\u00e9pouill\u00e8rent les victimes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35","name":"2 Chroniques 35","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.12","name":"2 Chroniques 35:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.10","name":"2 Chroniques 35:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.12","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 35:12","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.035.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.035.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.35.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Ils mirent \u00e0 part les holocaustes pour les donner aux diff\u00e9rentes maisons paternelles des gens du peuple, afin qu\u2019ils les offrissent \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, comme il est \u00e9crit dans le livre de Mo\u00efse; et de m\u00eame pour les b\u0153ufs.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35","name":"2 Chroniques 35","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.13","name":"2 Chroniques 35:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.11","name":"2 Chroniques 35:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.13","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 35:13","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.035.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.035.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.35.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Ils firent cuire la P\u00e2que au feu, selon l\u2019ordonnance, et ils firent cuire les choses saintes dans des chaudi\u00e8res, des chaudrons et des po\u00eales; et ils s\u2019empress\u00e8rent de les distribuer \u00e0 tout le peuple.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35","name":"2 Chroniques 35","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.14","name":"2 Chroniques 35:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.12","name":"2 Chroniques 35:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.14","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 35:14","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.035.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.035.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.35.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Ensuite ils pr\u00e9par\u00e8rent ce qui \u00e9tait pour eux et pour les sacrificateurs, car les sacrificateurs, fils d\u2019Aaron, furent occup\u00e9s jusqu\u2019\u00e0 la nuit \u00e0 offrir les holocaustes et les graisses; c\u2019est pourquoi les L\u00e9vites pr\u00e9par\u00e8rent pour eux et pour les sacrificateurs, fils d\u2019Aaron.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35","name":"2 Chroniques 35","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.15","name":"2 Chroniques 35:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.13","name":"2 Chroniques 35:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.15","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 35:15","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.035.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.035.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.35.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Les chantres, fils d\u2019Asaph, \u00e9taient \u00e0 leur place, selon l\u2019ordre de David, d\u2019Asaph, d\u2019H\u00e9man, et de Jeduthun le voyant du roi, et les portiers \u00e9taient \u00e0 chaque porte; ils n\u2019eurent pas \u00e0 se d\u00e9tourner de leur office, car leurs fr\u00e8res les L\u00e9vites pr\u00e9par\u00e8rent ce qui \u00e9tait pour eux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35","name":"2 Chroniques 35","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.16","name":"2 Chroniques 35:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.14","name":"2 Chroniques 35:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.16","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 35:16","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.035.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.035.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.35.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Ainsi fut organis\u00e9 ce jour-l\u00e0 tout le service de l\u2019\u00c9ternel pour faire la P\u00e2que et pour offrir des holocaustes sur l\u2019autel de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, d\u2019apr\u00e8s l\u2019ordre du roi Josias.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35","name":"2 Chroniques 35","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.17","name":"2 Chroniques 35:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.15","name":"2 Chroniques 35:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.17","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 35:17","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.035.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.035.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.35.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Les enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl qui se trouvaient l\u00e0 c\u00e9l\u00e9br\u00e8rent la P\u00e2que en ce temps et la f\u00eate des pains sans levain pendant sept jours.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35","name":"2 Chroniques 35","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.18","name":"2 Chroniques 35:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.16","name":"2 Chroniques 35:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.18","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 35:18","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.035.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.035.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.35.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Aucune P\u00e2que pareille \u00e0 celle-l\u00e0 n\u2019avait \u00e9t\u00e9 c\u00e9l\u00e9br\u00e9e en Isra\u00ebl depuis les jours de Samuel le proph\u00e8te; et aucun des rois d\u2019Isra\u00ebl n\u2019avait c\u00e9l\u00e9br\u00e9 une P\u00e2que pareille \u00e0 celle que c\u00e9l\u00e9br\u00e8rent Josias, les sacrificateurs et les L\u00e9vites, tout Juda et Isra\u00ebl qui s\u2019y trouvaient, et les habitants de J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35","name":"2 Chroniques 35","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.19","name":"2 Chroniques 35:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.17","name":"2 Chroniques 35:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.19","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 35:19","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.035.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.035.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.35.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Ce fut la dix-huiti\u00e8me ann\u00e9e du r\u00e8gne de Josias que cette P\u00e2que fut c\u00e9l\u00e9br\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35","name":"2 Chroniques 35","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.20","name":"2 Chroniques 35:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.18","name":"2 Chroniques 35:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.20","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 35:20","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.035.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.035.021,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Josias tu\u00e9 par les archers de N\u00e9co, roi d\u2019\u00c9gypte<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 20-27: cf. 2 R 23:26-30. J\u00e9 22:10, 15, 16. Ap 3:10.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.35.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Apr\u00e8s tout cela, apr\u00e8s que Josias eut r\u00e9par\u00e9 la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, N\u00e9co, roi d\u2019\u00c9gypte, monta pour combattre \u00e0 Carkemisch sur l\u2019Euphrate. Josias marcha \u00e0 sa rencontre;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35","name":"2 Chroniques 35","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.21","name":"2 Chroniques 35:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.19","name":"2 Chroniques 35:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.21","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 35:21","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.035.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.035.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.35.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>et N\u00e9co lui envoya des messagers pour dire: Qu\u2019y a-t-il entre moi et toi, roi de Juda? Ce n\u2019est pas contre toi que je viens aujourd\u2019hui; c\u2019est contre une maison avec laquelle je suis en guerre. Et Dieu m\u2019a dit de me h\u00e2ter. Ne t\u2019oppose pas \u00e0 Dieu, qui est avec moi, de peur qu\u2019il ne te d\u00e9truise.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35","name":"2 Chroniques 35","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.22","name":"2 Chroniques 35:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.20","name":"2 Chroniques 35:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.22","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 35:22","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.035.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.035.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.35.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Mais Josias ne se d\u00e9tourna point de lui, et il se d\u00e9guisa pour l\u2019attaquer, sans \u00e9couter les paroles de N\u00e9co, qui venaient de la bouche de Dieu. Il s\u2019avan\u00e7a pour combattre dans la vall\u00e9e de Meguiddo.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35","name":"2 Chroniques 35","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.23","name":"2 Chroniques 35:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.21","name":"2 Chroniques 35:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.23","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 35:23","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.035.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.035.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.35.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Les archers tir\u00e8rent sur le roi Josias, et le roi dit \u00e0 ses serviteurs: Emportez-moi, car je suis gravement bless\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35","name":"2 Chroniques 35","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.24","name":"2 Chroniques 35:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.22","name":"2 Chroniques 35:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.24","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 35:24","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.035.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.035.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.35.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Ses serviteurs l\u2019emport\u00e8rent du char, le mirent dans un second char qui \u00e9tait \u00e0 lui, et l\u2019amen\u00e8rent \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem. Il mourut, et fut enterr\u00e9 dans le s\u00e9pulcre de ses p\u00e8res. Tout Juda et J\u00e9rusalem pleur\u00e8rent Josias.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35","name":"2 Chroniques 35","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.25","name":"2 Chroniques 35:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.23","name":"2 Chroniques 35:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.25","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 35:25","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.035.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.035.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.35.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>J\u00e9r\u00e9mie fit une complainte sur Josias; tous les chanteurs et toutes les chanteuses ont parl\u00e9 de Josias dans leurs complaintes jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce jour, et en ont \u00e9tabli la coutume en Isra\u00ebl. Ces chants sont \u00e9crits dans les Complaintes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35","name":"2 Chroniques 35","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.26","name":"2 Chroniques 35:26","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.24","name":"2 Chroniques 35:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.26","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 35:26","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.035.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.035.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.35.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Le reste des actions de Josias, et ses \u0153uvres de pi\u00e9t\u00e9, telles que les prescrit la loi de l\u2019\u00c9ternel,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35","name":"2 Chroniques 35","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.27","name":"2 Chroniques 35:27","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.25","name":"2 Chroniques 35:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.27","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 35:27","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.035.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.036.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.35.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>ses premi\u00e8res et ses derni\u00e8res actions, cela est \u00e9crit dans le livre des rois d\u2019Isra\u00ebl et de Juda.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35","name":"2 Chroniques 35","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.36.1","name":"2 Chroniques 36:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.36.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.35.26","name":"2 Chroniques 35:26","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.35.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb9d83dd5.61738857');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb9d83dd5.61738857\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb9d83dd5.61738857","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb9d83dd5.61738857'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb9d83dd5.61738857\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}